title: 15 minutes of daily calls
info: 15 minutes of calls for 1 day at the price of 15 Afghanis. To activate, dial *233*3*1# and to deactivate, dial *233*3*2#.

title: 75 minutes of daily calls
info: 75  call minutes for 1 day at the price of 25 Afghanis. To activate, dial *233*1*1# and to deactivate *233*1*2#.
